One of the possibile use cases for HoneyTrap can be to simulate a device in your DMZ to &ldquo;attract&rdquo; potentials hackers. You could also simulate a device within another part of your network, for internals attacks.
In this scenario, we decided to simulate a web server in our DMZ. We actually did that on one of our domain, keep on reading to find out more.
